   "id": "4f093536-232b-407a-9b4d-438e432491b4",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "评价指标"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "raw",
   "id": "aa6bc3ad-c1f6-4de2-ad25-17af98209393",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "本次竞赛的评价标准采用F1_score，分数越高，效果越好。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "raw",
   "id": "53857f91-eef0-4591-98e6-3b6346b5cbf4",
